data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome home to this like new construction home! 4 bedroom / 2 bath, 1810 sq ft of living space, and a 2-Car Garage with NO rear neighbors. Charming open floor plan home on an oversized lot! Create lots of memories with friends and family in this home! For the chef in the family, enjoy the island in the kitchen with plenty of cabinetry and room to entertain! Enjoy a true walk in closet in the master bedroom. Sit outside in the back yard and watch the sunset with a spacious area for relaxation time. Looking for room for a pool & outdoor kitchen? This home has the space! **NO CDD** Fantastic location with easy access to dog parks, walking trails, shopping, restaurants and nature! Priced to sell! This will not last long!
